    "navbar": "Menu",
    "text": "Skip to main content\nQuick Links\nYour current preferred language is\nEnglish (United States)\nHome - City and County of Denver - Logo\nMenu\nSearch\nHome\nHot Topics\nHere are some of our most popular topics! These links will get updated to reflect what’s most relevant or as city services become more popular.\nBuilding Permits\nRent and Utility Assistance\nInmate Search\nE-Bike Rebates\nPay Parking Ticket\nResidential Rentals\nVoter Information\nSnow Removal\nSign up for City Updates\nTop Services\nAdopt A Pet\nCity Jobs\nMarriage & Civil Union Licenses\nProperty Information\nVehicle Registration\nWaste & Recycling Schedules\nFeatured Content\nConnect To Your City\nSolid Waste Service Changes\nMinimum Wage in 2023\nMigrant Sheltering Updates\nLatest From Denver\nNews\nSocial\nEvents\nDenver 8 TV\nCaring for Denver still allowed to use additional funds for operations\nPublished on January 05, 2023\nMayor Hancock Statement on Officer Indictment\nPublished on January 04, 2023\nDenver E-Bike and E-Cargo Bike Rebate Returns January 31\nPublished on January 04, 2023\nMayor Supporting State Efforts Helping Migrants Continue their Journey\nPublished on January 03, 2023\nDDPHE Issues Request for Proposals for Food System Resiliency Grant\nPublished on January 03, 2023\nLarimer Street Bridge Replacement to Create Better Connections\nPublished on January 03, 2023\nLarimer Bridge Replacement and Streetscaping to Create Connections\nPublished on January 03, 2023\nDenver City Council Schedule for the Week of January 2, 2023\nPublished on December 29, 2022\nTree Damage: How to Manage Broken Limbs & Fallen Branches\nPublished on December 29, 2022\nView More News\nPress left and right keys to move between tabs. Press down to focus tab content.\nWhat's Near Me?\nEnter your street address\nContact 3-1-1\nReport a Problem\nAsk a Question\nCall 3-1-1\nOutside Denver: (720) 913-1311\nHearing Impaired Only (TTY): (720) 913-8479\nFor Emergencies: 9-1-1\nVisit Other Denver Sites\nArts & Venues Denver\nDenver County Courts\nDenver Public Library\nDenver International Airport\nDenver Zoo\nVisit Denver\nShare & Connect\nThe Denver Local is your resource for\ncity news and information directly to your inbox.\nSign up to stay informed!\nFollow Us On Social\nFollow on Facebook\nInstagram\nFollow on Twitter\nYouTube\nNext Door\nCity Jobs | Accessibility | Privacy & Security | Terms of Use | Open Records (CORA)\n© 2023 City and County of Denver\nReady",
